name: ​* * I M P O S S I B L E * * BRICK BREAKER GAME (WebGL)
name_original: ​* * I M P O S S I B L E * * BRICK BREAKER GAME (WebGL)
description:
WebGL presentation of a game made in Unity Game Engine as part of learning Unity process. 

* * I M P O S S I B L E * * BRICK BREAKER GAME
Very hard, fast paced, 8 levels to pass trough and many keyboards and mice to break! 
Game is made as a practice in learning Unity Game Engine. This game is free!
